[{"title":"STM32-UART串口通信","date":"2020-07-22T08:43:51.000Z","path":"2020/07/stm32/2020-07-22-uart-io/","content":"<p>STM32-UART串口通信，日志输出，任意长度数据接收</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p><strong>代码实现环境</strong></p>\n<p>STM32型号：STM32F103RCT6</p>\n<p>STM32CubeMX配置：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>设置Connectivity的USART1的Mode为Asynchronous</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>勾选NVIC Settings的global interrupt的Enabled</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/07/22/vAcb9eRLjCiE4KY.jpg\" alt=\"CubeMX配置\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"实现printf及自定义log日志\"><a href=\"#实现printf及自定义log日志\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实现printf及自定义log日志\"></a>实现printf及自定义log日志</h2><figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/* Private define ------------------------------------------------------------*/</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/* USER CODE BEGIN PD */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">define</span> LOG_ENABLE 1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">if</span> LOG_ENABLE</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">define</span> log(format,...) printf(format<span class=\"string\">\"\\r\\n\"</span>,##__VA_ARGS__)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">else</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">define</span> log(format,...)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">endif</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">ifdef</span> __GNUC__</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">define</span> PUTCHAR_PROTOTYPE int __io_putchar(int ch)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">else</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">define</span> PUTCHAR_PROTOTYPE int fputc(int ch, FILE *f)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"meta-keyword\">endif</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">PUTCHAR_PROTOTYPE</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">// 参数1： 使用哪个usart</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">// 参数2： 字符，</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">// 参数3：输出数量，</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">// 参数4：超时等待时间</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  HAL_UART_Transmit(&amp;huart1 , (<span class=\"keyword\">uint8_t</span> *)&amp;ch, <span class=\"number\">1</span> , <span class=\"number\">0xffff</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> ch;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/* USER CODE END PD */</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"实现任意长度数据收发\"><a href=\"#实现任意长度数据收发\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实现任意长度数据收发\"></a>实现任意长度数据收发</h2><p>1、声明变量及回调函数</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br><span class=\"line\">52</span><br><span class=\"line\">53</span><br><span class=\"line\">54</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/* Private user code ---------------------------------------------------------*/</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/* USER CODE BEGIN 0 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">uint8_t</span> RECEIVE_ARRAY[<span class=\"number\">1024</span>] = &#123;<span class=\"number\">0</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">uint8_t</span> RxByte;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">uint8_t</span> RxBuff[<span class=\"number\">4096</span>];</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">uint16_t</span> Rx_Count;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">HAL_UART_RxCpltCallback</span><span class=\"params\">(UART_HandleTypeDef *huart)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">// 有串口消息进来, 这里就会执行</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//  if (USART1 == huart-&gt;Instance) &#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">////  char data[] = \"hello !!!\\r\\n\";</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//    // 把接收到的数据返回出去</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//    HAL_UART_Transmit(&amp;huart1, RECEIVE_ARRAY, sizeof RECEIVE_ARRAY, 1000);</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//    // 若想中断重复生效,这里需要重新定义</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//    HAL_UART_Receive_IT(&amp;huart1, RECEIVE_ARRAY, 1);</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//  &#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">/* Prevent unused argument(s) compilation warning */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  UNUSED(huart);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  RxBuff[Rx_Count++]=RxByte;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(RxByte == <span class=\"number\">0x0A</span> )</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 默认换行按\\n退一个字节</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> len = Rx_Count - <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 如果换行是\\r\\n则要多退一个字节</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (RxBuff[Rx_Count - <span class=\"number\">2</span>] == <span class=\"number\">0x0D</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      len = Rx_Count - <span class=\"number\">2</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">char</span> data[len];</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">strncpy</span>(data, RxBuff, len);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"built_in\">strncmp</span>(data, <span class=\"string\">\"test\"</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">sizeof</span> data) == <span class=\"number\">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"built_in\">log</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"ttttt!\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;<span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"built_in\">strncmp</span>(data, <span class=\"string\">\"good\"</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">sizeof</span> data) == <span class=\"number\">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"built_in\">printf</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"gggggggggggggggggggggggggggggggggggggggggggggggggggggggg!\\r\\n\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;<span class=\"keyword\">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      HAL_UART_Transmit(&amp;huart1, data, <span class=\"keyword\">sizeof</span> data, <span class=\"number\">3000</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">memset</span>(RxBuff, <span class=\"number\">0</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">sizeof</span> RxBuff);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    Rx_Count=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(Rx_Count&gt;=<span class=\"number\">4096</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">memset</span>(RxBuff, <span class=\"number\">0</span>, <span class=\"keyword\">sizeof</span> RxBuff);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    Rx_Count=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"comment\">// 循环接收每个字节</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(HAL_UART_Receive_IT(&amp;huart1,&amp;RxByte,<span class=\"number\">1</span>)==HAL_OK);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/* USER CODE END 0 */</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>2、在<code>MX_USART1_UART_Init();</code>后添加 中断接收代码</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">/* USER CODE BEGIN 2 */</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 开启中断, 并将接收到的数据放到 RxByte 里</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">HAL_UART_Receive_IT(&amp;huart1, &amp;RxByte, <span class=\"number\">1</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>3、测试发个欢迎消息给客户端</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">char</span> data[] = <span class=\"string\">\"hello world!\\r\\n\"</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 参数1： 使用哪个usart</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 参数2： 要发送的字符</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 参数3： 输出长度</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 参数4： 超时等待时间</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">HAL_UART_Transmit(&amp;huart1, data, <span class=\"built_in\">strlen</span>(data), <span class=\"number\">3000</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">printf</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"test: %d, %f \\r\\n\"</span>, <span class=\"number\">123</span>, <span class=\"number\">11.12345</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">log</span>(<span class=\"string\">\"test log!\"</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>4、如果想要使用printf输出浮点数的话，还需要做如下配置：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>修改CMakeLIst文件，追加<code>-u _printf_float</code></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight cmake\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">SET</span>(COMMON_FLAGS</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">\"-mcpu=cortex-m3 $&#123;FPU_FLAGS&#125; -mthumb -mthumb-interwork -ffunction-sections -fdata-sections \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">    -g -fno-common -fmessage-length=0 -specs=nosys.specs -specs=nano.specs -u _printf_float\"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>如果仍然无法输出浮点数,就拷贝下面文件到Src目录中</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight gradle\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">~<span class=\"regexp\">/STM32Cube/</span>Repository<span class=\"regexp\">/STM32Cube_FW_F1_V1.8.0/</span>Projects<span class=\"regexp\">/STM3210C_EVAL/</span>Examples<span class=\"regexp\">/UART/U</span>ART_Printf<span class=\"regexp\">/syscalls.c</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>这是因为我们所使用的库，默认是没有开启浮点数输出的.这里需要注意的是我们修改的是CubeMX工具自动生成的CMakeList,当我们重新使用CubeMX重新生成代码的时候,这里所做的所有修改都将会丢失.</p>\n<p>注意:改动完成之后,请在Clion中Tools–&gt;Cmake–&gt;Reset Cache and Reload Project</p>\n<p><strong>实现效果</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/07/22/mubvDyaRqeL53cH.png\" alt=\"输入输出演示\"></p>\n","excerpt":"STM32-UART串口通信，日志输出，任意长度数据接收","categories":[{"name":"技术开发","slug":"技术开发","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/categories/技术开发/"}],"tags":[{"name":"STM32","slug":"STM32","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/tags/STM32/"}]},{"title":"2020一年之计（庚子鼠年）","date":"2020-02-09T12:13:33.000Z","path":"2020/02/2020-02-09-ynzj/","content":"<p>​    一年之计在于春，又到了一年一度的年底打脸手册撰写季，今年2020开年我们国家将近春节的时候，爆发了一场全国范围的流感，同时，偶像科比的去世，注定了这一年的不平凡。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<ul>\n<li><p>赚钱</p>\n<p>在任何兴趣爱好之前，首先要考虑的问题，是家人和自己的基本生活状态。对于家人，不言而喻，妻子的生活质量，孩子的教育和快乐，虽说跟金钱无关，但坦白讲钱能带来更高密度的幸福与快乐（在认为幸福感有差异的前提下）。对于自己也一样，在出租屋中打游戏，还是自己的独栋别墅中打游戏，得到的快乐真的是不同的。前者不管打赢了输了，总会觉得自己在荒废时间，后者，才谈得上在享受游戏。</p>\n<p>今年我同样应当专注于从自己所擅长的方向去创收。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>写作</p>\n<p>虽然现在作为IT培训的讲师，但我很多时候仍然将自己定位为一个程序员，保持开发的思想，保持学习新技术的动力。故而，写作应该包括代码的编写，输出到github开源平台，以及实际意义上个人写作，输出到自己的博客，技术上的写作，输出到自己的博客和公众博客平台。</p>\n<p>读书是保持长期高质量的写作的前提，同样也能提高我本职工作的表达能力，语言组织能力。不断的写作，帮助我凝练语言，用最直观贴切的语言，描述抽象的知识概念。</p>\n<p>写作短期来看，是一段真正意义上的思考，可以帮助我们静下来咀嚼最近的事情，等同于吾日三省吾身的效果。长期来看，稳定有效的输出，是个人实力的积累，在当下程序员的行当，个人的能力隐藏在两个地方，一个是我们写的代码，一个是我们脑海里的编程思想。不骄傲的说，程序员很多时候，会像硅谷钢铁侠——马斯克，表达自己的想法的时候磕磕巴巴（参考<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/av65925736\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">2019世界人工智能大会—马云对话马斯克</a>），但是脑子里又确实有大量的存货，可以称之为嘴巴跟不上思想。所以，当一个行业内的人想了解你的时候，能够读到并读懂你代码的人屈指可数，但是一个清晰明了的博客链接，却是他深入了解你的极佳方式。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>篮球</p>\n<p>锻炼身体，控制体重，加强对身体大肌肉的控制能力。</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>作为宝宝的榜样，身体和思想都要在路上。</p>\n<p>我还有诸多对生活的期待：游戏、钢琴、吉他、摄影、散打、厨艺、围棋、健身、旅游</p>\n","excerpt":"​ 一年之计在于春，又到了一年一度的年底打脸手册撰写季，今年2020开年我们国家将近春节的时候，爆发了一场全国范围的流感，同时，偶像科比的去世，注定了这一年的不平凡。","categories":[{"name":"日常生活","slug":"日常生活","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/categories/日常生活/"}],"tags":[{"name":"生活","slug":"生活","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/tags/生活/"}]},{"title":"人是否应该为知道的太多而烦恼","date":"2019-03-22T04:42:46.000Z","path":"2019/03/2019-03-22-zddtd/","content":"<p>​    以前的我会执着的认为，人不应该因为自己知道的太多而烦恼，现在的我认为，这或许是一种固执的想法。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>​    每个人的精力是有限的，当我们掌握了过多的正面或负面的信息之后，并不一定能对我们的判断有更好的促进，更多的信息意味着我们很可能会迷失在对细节的追逐，而这往往会影响我们做出最贴近直觉的判断。对信息的获取或屏蔽，是每个人在处理不同问题时的不同方式。我们不能一味的无知，也不能一味的求知。</p>\n<p>​    </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://poplartang.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/blog/2019-04/zddd.jpg?x-oss-process=image/resize,m_lfit,w_300,h_600\" alt=\"知道的太多\"></p>\n<p>​    但是，理智又会告诉我们，对这个世界的真想了解的越多，我们越能在危机即将来临时，做好该有的准备，不至于认为一切都是命。</p>\n<p>​    因为更多的信息往往带来的是痛苦——“知道的越多，痛苦就越多”。</p>\n<p>​    比如这些事情：我们永远不知道也不希望知道，快递外卖的原材料来源有多奇怪，制作过程有多么混乱，安全卫生有多简陋，我们宁愿固执相信自己吃下的披萨经过了严格的安全检验。我们不需要，也不必知道同事工资，如果自己的心态不好，那带不来任何益处，只能带来傲慢与偏见。对个人而言，疾病是我们必须正确面对及认识的事情，定期体检十分必要，然而依然有很多人，身上出现了极大的不适，才去医院检查身体。仿佛这种不适只是不幸运，跟自己的经历毫无关系，关于身体的信息，我们提早知道，掌握的越多，就能避免越多的风险。</p>\n<p>​    一个良好的心态很重要，以应对各种突如其来的事件，知道的越多，在作出决策的时候，权衡的利弊就越全面。有些事情我们不知道，并不代表没发生。还有一些事情，正因为我们害怕了解，而无法真正了解，由此造成了一些本可以解决和规避的问题无法提前做预案，那才是更加可悲的存在，完全无法体现出人的主观能动性和意志力。</p>\n<p>​    在现如今的信息爆炸的世界，可能我们绝大多数人处在前两个状态：沉浸在鸟语花香的围墙中，在围墙边缘看到了世界的残破不堪。在心底里保持一个信仰：太阳照常升起，乌云总会散去。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://poplartang.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/blog/2019-04/zddtd.jpg\" alt=\"拨开天空的乌云\"></p>\n","excerpt":"​ 以前的我会执着的认为，人不应该因为自己知道的太多而烦恼，现在的我认为，这或许是一种固执的想法。","categories":[{"name":"所思所想","slug":"所思所想","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/categories/所思所想/"}],"tags":[{"name":"瞎想","slug":"瞎想","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/tags/瞎想/"}]},{"title":"日常生活营养食谱（不定期更新）","date":"2018-04-13T09:32:07.000Z","path":"2018/04/2018-04-13-YYSP/","content":"<p>每个食材都有它独特的味道，每味佐料都有它特殊的用处，味蕾不同的体验和饱腹感是健康的保障，也是幸福的来源。每天的家庭生活都是要重复做很多菜，这里做个记录，以便不断优化菜品。认真对待做菜就是认真对待生活。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>说明：以下菜品食材部分，为了避免重复，省去油和盐这种必备的描述，在步骤里会有所体现。</p>\n<h2 id=\"下饭菜\"><a href=\"#下饭菜\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下饭菜\"></a>下饭菜</h2><h3 id=\"酸辣土豆丝\"><a href=\"#酸辣土豆丝\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"酸辣土豆丝\"></a>酸辣土豆丝</h3><blockquote>\n<p>好的下饭菜，往往使用的都是最简单的食材</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><p>食材：</p>\n<p>土豆2个，蒜瓣2瓣、小葱3根，小红椒2根、生抽</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>步骤：</p>\n<p>土豆削皮擦丝儿，用清水淘三遍去淀粉防粘锅（<strong>这一步不能忘</strong>），泡上水；蒜2瓣切末，小葱三根切碎，2根小红椒切碎，锅放油，把土豆丝水倒出，等烧热微微冒烟，下蒜末，倒土豆丝，翻炒，下小红椒碎末。放生抽，食盐，葱花，出锅。香喷喷，隔壁老王都流口水！</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"西红柿炒蛋\"><a href=\"#西红柿炒蛋\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"西红柿炒蛋\"></a>西红柿炒蛋</h3><blockquote>\n<p>这个是真的香，奇怪为什么西红柿和番茄会这么般配</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><p>食材：</p>\n<p>西红柿2个，鸡蛋2个，砂糖，葱花，蒜瓣</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>步骤：</p>\n<p>西红柿切块（有时间可以先用开水烫下，扒了皮），撒糖（<strong>这一步不能忘</strong>，撒多少看你手感），俩鸡蛋打碗里搅拌一下，锅里放油烧温热，倒鸡蛋液，等一会儿凝固了点再翻炒，放葱白和蒜瓣，把鸡蛋推在锅的一边，倒入西红柿，用铲子捣成小块，让西红柿汁流出来跟鸡蛋大和谐，翻炒，看锅突然冒出一股热气，放盐，翻两下出锅。美滋滋，一盘菜下两碗饭。</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>酸辣白菜</p>\n<p>青椒炒肉</p>\n<p>韭菜苔炒蛋</p>\n<p>秋葵炒鸡蛋</p>\n<p>可乐鸡翅</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>收汁，收汁，一定要收汁</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>辣子鸡/鸭</p>\n<p>红烧茄子</p>\n<p>辣炒花蛤</p>\n<p>黄焖鸡 (会吃不会做)</p>\n<p>红烧鱼</p>\n<p>肉末豆角</p>\n<p>宫保鸡丁 (会吃不会做)</p>\n<p>孜然牛肉土豆片 (会吃不会做)</p>\n<p>手撕包菜 (会吃不会做)</p>\n<p>干锅菜花 (会吃不会做)</p>\n<h2 id=\"凉菜\"><a href=\"#凉菜\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"凉菜\"></a>凉菜</h2><p>凉拌黄瓜</p>\n<p>凉拌海带丝</p>\n<p>凉拌木耳</p>\n<h2 id=\"煲汤\"><a href=\"#煲汤\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"煲汤\"></a>煲汤</h2><p>鱼头汤/鲫鱼汤</p>\n<p>小鸡炖蘑菇</p>\n<p>冬瓜排骨汤</p>\n<p>[紫菜]西红柿蛋汤</p>\n<h2 id=\"面食\"><a href=\"#面食\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"面食\"></a>面食</h2><h3 id=\"鸡蛋面疙瘩\"><a href=\"#鸡蛋面疙瘩\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"鸡蛋面疙瘩\"></a>鸡蛋面疙瘩</h3><blockquote>\n<p>配合咸菜，可作为早晚餐，相当美滋滋！</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><p>食材：</p>\n<p>面粉，鸡蛋1-2个</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>步骤：</p>\n<p>起锅上水烧开，烧水过程中，面粉掺凉水搅和成面浆，能稍微挂筷即可，鸡蛋打散备用。</p>\n<p>水烧开后，倒入面浆水，边倒边用筷子搅和锅。开大火煮开后，转小火，倒入鸡蛋，搅和搅和，2分钟后关火开吃。</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"焖面\"><a href=\"#焖面\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"焖面\"></a>焖面</h3><blockquote>\n<p>适合午饭晚饭，吃的时候就上大蒜，香喷喷！</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><p>食材：</p>\n<p>肉丝，扁豆角，面条（干湿均可）</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>步骤：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>肉切似，豆角切中段。锅下油，油热下肉丝，炒至肉表面泛焦黄，放葱、蒜、生抽，倒入豆角，煸炒。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>加热水至没过菜。水烧开后转小火，将面条均匀盖在菜上，在面上稍撒生抽，盖锅盖，焖10分钟，关火。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>开盖，用筷子将面和菜拌匀即可，盛碗开吃。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>番茄鸡蛋面</p>\n","excerpt":"每个食材都有它独特的味道，每味佐料都有它特殊的用处，味蕾不同的体验和饱腹感是健康的保障，也是幸福的来源。每天的家庭生活都是要重复做很多菜，这里做个记录，以便不断优化菜品。认真对待做菜就是认真对待生活。","categories":[{"name":"日常生活","slug":"日常生活","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/categories/日常生活/"}],"tags":[{"name":"生活","slug":"生活","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/tags/生活/"}]},{"title":"思维反射&肌肉反射","date":"2018-04-11T05:25:56.000Z","path":"2018/04/思维反射/","content":"<p>将学习过程和能力形成的过程进行分析，在进行新技能的认知过程中，我们可以有迹可循，从而通过形成快速认知习惯加快认知过程本身。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>我们不断的学习, 目标可以分为三个阶段：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>进行长久的记忆存储</li>\n<li>讲这些记忆进行关联</li>\n<li>将这些新的关联体进行再次存储</li>\n</ol>\n<p>步骤2可以帮我们理解认知我们学接触到的信息，步骤3是推动这个世界的源力，我们的知识正是千百年来一代一代的人的结晶，通过各种形式把步骤3形成的新关联体以各种形式记录下来。所以我们都是站在巨人的肩膀上。</p>\n<p>社交天才和运动天才在抽象层面上说，其机理几乎如出一辙：一个是思维记忆，另一个是肌肉记忆。前者可以让我们思考更迅速、全面，或者可以让我们反应更灵敏、有节奏感。</p>\n","excerpt":"将学习过程和能力形成的过程进行分析，在进行新技能的认知过程中，我们可以有迹可循，从而通过形成快速认知习惯加快认知过程本身。","categories":[{"name":"所思所想","slug":"所思所想","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/categories/所思所想/"}],"tags":[{"name":"瞎想","slug":"瞎想","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/tags/瞎想/"}]},{"title":"ReactJS - day01 入门知识","date":"2018-04-10T17:14:08.000Z","path":"2018/04/ReactJS-day01/","content":"<p>介绍React开发环境的初始化，主要包括：组件定义、props属性、state状态、组件生命周期、事件处理</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h2 id=\"React环境初始化\"><a href=\"#React环境初始化\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"React环境初始化\"></a>React环境初始化</h2><h3 id=\"入门介绍\"><a href=\"#入门介绍\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"入门介绍:\"></a>入门介绍:</h3><blockquote>\n<p>声明式：数据驱动</p>\n<p>组件化：把相似的代码放到一起进行复用，传递数据</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><h4 id=\"官网\"><a href=\"#官网\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"官网:\"></a>官网:</h4></li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>英文:<a href=\"https://reactjs.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">https://reactjs.org/</a></p>\n<p>中文:<a href=\"https://doc.react-china.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">https://doc.react-china.org/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"方式一-脚手架-快捷、稳定\"><a href=\"#方式一-脚手架-快捷、稳定\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"方式一: 脚手架 (快捷、稳定)\"></a>方式一: 脚手架 (快捷、稳定)</h3><ul>\n<li>官方教程: <a href=\"https://doc.react-china.org/docs/add-react-to-a-new-app.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">参考链接1</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/create-react-app#create-react-app-\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">参考链接2</a></li>\n<li><p>执行命令:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install -g create-react-app</span><br><span class=\"line\">create-react-app my-app</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> my-app</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm start</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 或使用以下命令 If you have npm 5.2.0+ installed, you may use npx instead.</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">npx create-react-app my-app</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> my-app</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm start</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"方式二-Webpack-步骤较多按下不表\"><a href=\"#方式二-Webpack-步骤较多按下不表\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"方式二:  Webpack (步骤较多按下不表)\"></a>方式二:  Webpack (步骤较多按下不表)</h3><h2 id=\"元素渲染\"><a href=\"#元素渲染\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"元素渲染\"></a>元素渲染</h2><p>元素是构成 React 应用的最小单位。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> element = <span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">h1</span>&gt;</span>Hello, world<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">h1</span>&gt;</span></span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>渲染元素</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">'react'</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> ReactDOM <span class=\"keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"string\">'react-dom'</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> element = <span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">h1</span>&gt;</span>Hello, world<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">h1</span>&gt;</span></span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">ReactDOM.render(</span><br><span class=\"line\">  element,</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"built_in\">document</span>.getElementById(<span class=\"string\">'root'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<p>React和ReactDOM为以下入口文件代码默认导包</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"组件及组件状态\"><a href=\"#组件及组件状态\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"组件及组件状态\"></a>组件及组件状态</h2><p>组件可以将界面分割成一些的独立的、可复用的组成部分，我们只需专注于构建每一个单独的部分。按钮，对话框，列表，输入框都是组件。</p>\n<p>组件从概念上看就像是函数，它可以接收任意的输入值（称之为“props”），并返回一个需要在页面上展示的React元素。</p>\n<h3 id=\"函数定义组件-无状态\"><a href=\"#函数定义组件-无状态\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"函数定义组件(无状态)\"></a>函数定义组件(无状态)</h3><p>JavaScript函数</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title\">Hello</span>(<span class=\"params\">props</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">h1</span>&gt;</span>Hi, &#123;props.name&#125;<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">h1</span>&gt;</span></span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"类定义组件-有状态\"><a href=\"#类定义组件-有状态\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"类定义组件(有状态)\"></a>类定义组件(有状态)</h3><p><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Classes\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">class由es6支持</a></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Hello</span> <span class=\"keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"title\">React</span>.<span class=\"title\">Component</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    render() &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   \t\t<span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">h1</span>&gt;</span>Hi, &#123;this.props.name&#125;<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">h1</span>&gt;</span></span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>以上两个组件效果在React中相同</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>注意： <strong>组件名首字母必须大写</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"组合组件\"><a href=\"#组合组件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"组合组件\"></a>组合组件</h3><p>组件之间可以相互引用, 通常把App组件作为根组件。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title\">App</span>(<span class=\"params\">props</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> (</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &lt;h1&gt;&#123;props.team&#125;&lt;/h1&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &lt;p&gt;成立时间: &#123;props.date.toLocaleString()&#125;&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &lt;p&gt;成员&#123;props.count&#125;&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;Hello name=\"悟空\" /&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;Hello name=\"三藏\" /&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;Hello name=\"八戒\" /&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &lt;Hello name=\"沙僧\" /&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    );</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">ReactDOM.render(</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &lt;App team=\"西天取经团\" date=&#123;new Date()&#125; count=&#123;4&#125;/&gt;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    document.getElementById('root')</span><br><span class=\"line\">);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<p>可在Chrome安装React插件查看结构</p>\n<p>注意：<strong>组件的返回值只能有一个根元素, 所以用一个div包裹所有Hello元素</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"Props-属性\"><a href=\"#Props-属性\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Props 属性\"></a>Props 属性</h3><blockquote>\n<p>props有两种输入方式：<strong>字符串“”</strong> ， <strong>大括号{}</strong></p>\n<p>props不可修改，<strong>属性只读</strong>， 强行修改会报错</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"State-状态\"><a href=\"#State-状态\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"State 状态\"></a>State 状态</h3><h4 id=\"自动更新时钟\"><a href=\"#自动更新时钟\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"自动更新时钟\"></a>自动更新时钟</h4><figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title\">tick</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">const</span> element = (</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">h1</span>&gt;</span>时钟<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">h1</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">h2</span>&gt;</span>current: &#123;new Date().toLocaleString()&#125;<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">h2</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    )</span><br><span class=\"line\">    ReactDOM.render(</span><br><span class=\"line\">        element,</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">document</span>.getElementById(<span class=\"string\">'root'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    );</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">setInterval(tick, <span class=\"number\">1000</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<p>应用一般只进行一次<code>ReactDOM.render()</code>渲染</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>封装时钟</li>\n<li>函数-&gt;类 / 定义局部状态属性</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Clock</span> <span class=\"keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"title\">React</span>.<span class=\"title\">Component</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">constructor</span>(props) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">super</span>(props);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.state = &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            date: <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"built_in\">Date</span>(),</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        setInterval(() =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.tick()</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;, <span class=\"number\">1000</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    tick() &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 更新date</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.setState(&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            date: <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"built_in\">Date</span>()</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    render() &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> (</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">h1</span>&gt;</span>Hi, clock Component state new!<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">h1</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">h2</span>&gt;</span>current: &#123;this.state.date.toLocaleString()&#125;<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">h2</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        );</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">ReactDOM.render(</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">Clock</span> /&gt;</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    document.getElementById('root')</span><br><span class=\"line\">);</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>state只能在构造函数初始化 <code>this.state={...}</code></li>\n<li>通过<code>this.setState({...})</code>更新并渲染组件</li>\n<li>调用<code>setState</code>时， React会将新的state合并到当前的state中</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"组件生命周期\"><a href=\"#组件生命周期\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"组件生命周期\"></a>组件生命周期</h2><p><img src=\"https://poplartang.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/FrontEnd/React%E4%B8%AD%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%9F.png\" alt=\"React中组件的生命周期\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>在componentDidMount初始化任务</p>\n<p>在componentWillUnmount清理任务</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"事件处理\"><a href=\"#事件处理\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"事件处理\"></a>事件处理</h2><h3 id=\"函数定义组件\"><a href=\"#函数定义组件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"函数定义组件\"></a>函数定义组件</h3><figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title\">ActionButton</span>(<span class=\"params\"></span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title\">handleClick</span>(<span class=\"params\">e</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"string\">'The Button was clicked.'</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> (</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">button</span> <span class=\"attr\">onClick</span>=<span class=\"string\">&#123;handleClick&#125;</span>&gt;</span>按我<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">button</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    );</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"类定义组件\"><a href=\"#类定义组件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"类定义组件\"></a>类定义组件</h3><ul>\n<li>注意以下两种写法的区别</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">App</span> <span class=\"keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"title\">React</span>.<span class=\"title\">Component</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    handleClick(e)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(<span class=\"string\">\"handleClick!\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    render() &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> (</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">button</span> <span class=\"attr\">onClick</span>=<span class=\"string\">&#123;this.handleClick&#125;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                        按钮1 &#123;'&#123;this.handleClick&#125;'&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">button</span>&gt;</span>\t\t\t\t   </span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">button</span> <span class=\"attr\">onClick</span>=<span class=\"string\">&#123;()</span> =&gt;</span> this.handleClick()&#125;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        按钮2 箭头函数 &#123;\"&#123;() =&gt; this.handleClick()&#125;\"&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">button</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span>  </span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">div</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        );</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<p>默认语法：类的方法默认不会绑定 this，也就是说在handleClick内部的this为undefined</p>\n<p>箭头式语法：在每次App渲染时都会创建一个新的回调函数，可能会造成子组件的额外渲染</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>默认语法this问题解决方案：事件绑定 / 属性初始化器语法：</li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li><p>在<strong>构造函数绑定</strong>this</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">constructor</span>(props) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">super</span>(props);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.handleClick = <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.handleClick.bind(<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>使用 <strong>属性初始化器</strong> 语法 声明handleClick</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">handleClick = () =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.setState(preState =&gt; (&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        count: preState.count + <span class=\"number\">1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;))</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ul>\n<li>计数器游戏</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"注意事项：\"><a href=\"#注意事项：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"注意事项：\"></a>注意事项：</h2><ul>\n<li><p>组件名首字母必须大写</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>组件的返回值只能有一个根元素</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>props属性是只读的</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","excerpt":"介绍React开发环境的初始化，主要包括：组件定义、props属性、state状态、组件生命周期、事件处理","categories":[{"name":"技术开发","slug":"技术开发","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/categories/技术开发/"}],"tags":[{"name":"前端","slug":"前端","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/tags/前端/"},{"name":"React","slug":"React","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/tags/React/"}]},{"title":"关于神是否存在的思考","date":"2017-06-08T01:27:48.000Z","path":"2017/06/关于神的存在/","content":"<p>面对未知，人们总会善于做出归纳总结，也许这样会带来安全感。未知的东西也许如薛定谔的猫一样，在盒子未打开之前，猫如同真相一样是处于生和死的叠加态的。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h2 id=\"你说神不存在\"><a href=\"#你说神不存在\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"你说神不存在?\"></a>你说神不存在?</h2><p>最常用的反驳类似于</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>一个全能的个体能够创造一块连他自己都搬不动的石头吗？</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>但也许对话会是这样的:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">我：你能创造出一块你举不起来的石头吗？</span><br><span class=\"line\">真正的神：能啊，我这就造一个</span><br><span class=\"line\">（石头凭空出现）</span><br><span class=\"line\">真正的神：这就是我举不起来的石头</span><br><span class=\"line\">我：你能把这块你举不起来的石头举起来吗？</span><br><span class=\"line\">真正的神：能啊，你看我给你举一个</span><br><span class=\"line\">（举起来了）</span><br><span class=\"line\">我：你不是说你举不起来吗？！</span><br><span class=\"line\">真正的神：我确实举不起来</span><br><span class=\"line\">我：可是你举起来了！</span><br><span class=\"line\">真正的神：是的，我可以随我的主观意愿做到或做不到所有事情</span><br><span class=\"line\">我：什么TM是的，这在逻辑上根本就说不通！！！</span><br><span class=\"line\">真正的神：用不着说通，逻辑也是我创造的</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"你说神存在\"><a href=\"#你说神存在\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"你说神存在?\"></a>你说神存在?</h2><p>如果神希望大家都信奉、臣服、敬畏祂。那只需要简单的彰显一下自己的与众不同即可。神为何只创造并观察这个世界，不去做任何干扰？比如明目张胆的显示神迹</p>\n<p>如果祂的存在是唯一的，祂为什么默许人类在世间对其进行各种胡编乱造</p>\n<p>如果神的慈爱的，纵观历史长河，何来天地不仁以万物为刍狗</p>\n<h2 id=\"叠加态\"><a href=\"#叠加态\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"叠加态\"></a>叠加态</h2><p>这个世界的魅力之一在于一些终极问题在长的时间维度上没有定论，人们在不断从各种角度试探、攻克才精雕细琢出世界的<strong>真相</strong>。</p>\n","excerpt":"面对未知，人们总会善于做出归纳总结，也许这样会带来安全感。未知的东西也许如薛定谔的猫一样，在盒子未打开之前，猫如同真相一样是处于生和死的叠加态的。","categories":[{"name":"所思所想","slug":"所思所想","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/categories/所思所想/"}],"tags":[{"name":"瞎想","slug":"瞎想","permalink":"http://tangyang.studio/tags/瞎想/"}]}]